# Products

## Get All Products

```php
$api_client->get('products', [
  'query' => [
    'page' => 4,
    'limit' => 50,
    'name' => 'Win',
    'productIds' => [ 1, 4, 7, 8 ],
    'updatedSince' => '2000-04-03 00:00:00'
  ]
]);
```

